  <title>Comparing Two Groups: Data Wrangling, Visualization, and t-Tests</title>

  <introduction>
    <p>
      This chapter covers techniques for comparing two groups, including data
      wrangling, visualization, and hypothesis testing with t-tests. You will
      learn how to determine whether observed differences between groups are
      statistically meaningful.
